strings.content: Here it is, the tower, according to the map.
按照地图指示，应该就是这座塔
The atmosphere is a little weird, Seems to be a lot of monsters. I must be careful forward it
感觉气氛有点诡异，里面似乎有不少魔物，小心前进吧
Woooow, what the hell is this?
Seems not very friendly. I have to be vigilant.
呵呵，又来了一个挑战者。
Who are you? Why are you here?
您是谁？为什么会在这里？
